{
  "arquivo": "ed06_02_05",
  "total": 59,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(This is the place she specified.\\n Somewhere around here%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...Found her!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...It's you, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Eh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku, it's you, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "H-hey?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Stay away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(This must be Miku.\\n If it really is her,\\n then this is even more...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Why can't I go to you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I'm making a weird face right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I'm so beyond happy,\\nthat I feel like I'm going crazy...\\nSo, I'm definitely making a weird face.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I don't want you to see me like this.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "D-don't!\\nDon't come over here!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Are you crying?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's just... I couldn't hold it back...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Sorry for making you wait.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, are you really happy with me%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...No, that's not it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro.\\nGive me your answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "My answer... What do you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You've forgotten, haven't you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "S-sorry.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You haven't given me an answer\\nabout the aquarium yet.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(The aquarium... Was it when we went there\\n together before the school festival?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I told you properly.\\nNow it's your turn, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You understand, right?\\nBecause telling everyone, 'I won't choose anyone' doesn't count.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're absolutely right.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "To me, you're special, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "That means...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Of course, I don't mean it in a weird way.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WOAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You were so slow...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I'm really sorry.\\nI've kept you waiting for so long.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, it's been almost half a year of waiting.\\nThoroughly reflect on that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, I really do feel bad about it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "If you had given me that answer half a year ago,\\nit would have been better.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Then, we could have gone to school together,\\nmade each other's bento for lunch, and%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "We could have done more things as lovers\\nwhile we were still in high school.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...That's true.\\nIf I hadn't hesitated with my answer,\\nwe could have spent that kind of time together.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "There were so many things I wanted to do with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "There was Christmas, New Year's Eve, and New Year's Day.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I wanted to make you even more delicious chocolates\\nfor Valentine's Day than last year.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I've made you wait for a long time, it seems.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "That's because there were your exams,\\nIchika's graduation, and other things.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I didn't want to wait, but...\\nI've been patient all this time.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "So from now on, I'll be more demanding.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nWe've gotta make up for lost time%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "We'll be together from now on.\\nI'll say it as many times as you like.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Okay, I'll do that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Accept all of me, okay?\\nFutaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}